'''''Heart of Men''''' (Yongeye gusubizwa muri Nollywood '''''nk'imbuto zibujijwe''''' na Henrikesim Multimedia Concept for International distribution) ni filime ishimishije yo muri Gana no muri [[Nijeriya]] yo mu 2009 yakozwe & iyobowe na Frank Rajah Arase, ikinwamo na Majid Michel, John Dumelo, igikomangoma David Osei na Yvonne Nelson . Yakiriye nomination eshanu muri Awards ya 6 ya Afrika Movie Academy Awards .

