== Kwakira ==
Muri rusange iyi filime yanenzwe guteza imbere ubwambure muri firime no kumenyekanisha amashusho yoroheje kuri [[Nigeriya]] na [[Gana]] yo mu rugo.   

Yashyizwe ku rutonde rw'inyenyeri 3 kuri 5 kuri Nollywood Reinvented yashimye ubuziranenge, imiterere n'amanota ya muzika, ariko ugasanga umugambi utoroshye kandi amashusho yimibonano mpuzabitsina yarenze.
